Syntax: readaura <target>

Psychically read a target's aura, revealing their true race and power
level to you alone. This pierces disguises: it works even on someone
currently displaying as another race or shielded by an appearance
override, and even if you have never introduced, been introduced, or
remembered them.

This is a one-time read, not a relationship change. It does not add
the target to your known list, does not reveal their name, and shows
nothing to anyone else in the room.

Costs ISP (read aura power). The generic 'psi'/'cast' dispatch
commands require a known target and will refuse a stranger, so always
use readaura directly:
  readaura human
  readaura Splynncryth

See also: psi, psionics, remoteview, introduce, remember, known
